code: var validate=function validate(values){var errors={};if(!values.username){errors.username='Required';}else if(values.username.length>15){errors.username="It's too long, less then 15";}if(!values.email){errors.email='Required';}else if(!/^[A-Z0-9._%+-]+@[A-Z0-9.-]+\.[A-Z]{2,4}$/i.test(values.email)){errors.email='Invalid email address';}if(!values.password){errors.password='Required';}else if(values.password.length<9){errors.password="It's too short, more then 9";}else if(values.password.length>15){errors.password="It's too long, less then 15";}return errors;};export default validate;
